casebody.head_matter:
In Re Walter Leroy MOODY, Jr., petitioner.
No. 17-8530 (17A1139).
Supreme Court of the United States
April 19, 2018.
Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of mandamus denied.
